Datasource.Parameter: (select way,landuse,man_made,military,"natural",power,name,highway from planet_osm_polygon where landuse is not null or "natural" in ('field','beach','desert','heath','mud','grassland','wood','sand','scrub') or highway in ('services','rest_area') order by z_order,way_area desc ) as leisure
(select way from planet_osm_line where man_made='cutline' ) as leisure
(select way,waterway from planet_osm_line where waterway in ('stream','drain','ditch') and (tunnel is null or tunnel != 'yes') ) as water_lines

(select way,"natural",waterway,landuse,name from planet_osm_polygon where (waterway in ('dock','mill_pond','riverbank','canal') or landuse in ('reservoir','water','basin') or "natural" in ('lake','water','land','glacier','mud','bay')) order by z_order,way_area desc ) as water_areas
(select way,"natural" from planet_osm_polygon where "natural" in ('marsh','wetland') order by z_order,way_area desc ) as water_areas
(select way,waterway from planet_osm_line where waterway='river' ) as water_lines

(select way,waterway,disused,lock,name, case when tunnel in ('yes','true','1') then 'yes'::text else tunnel end as tunnel from planet_osm_line where waterway in ('weir','river','canal','derelict_canal','stream','drain','ditch','wadi') and (bridge is null or bridge not in ('yes','true','1','aqueduct')) order by z_order ) as water_lines
(select way,name from planet_osm_line where waterway='dam') as dam

(select way,highway from planet_osm_line where highway in ('motorway','motorway_link','trunk','trunk_link','primary','primary_link','secondary','secondary_link','tertiary','tertiary_link','residential','unclassified') and tunnel in ('yes','true','1') order by z_order) as roads

(select distinct on (p.way) p.way as way,l.highway as int_tc_type from planet_osm_point p join planet_osm_line l on ST_DWithin(p.way,l.way,0.1) join (values ('tertiary',1), ('unclassified',2), ('residential',3), ('living_street',4), ('service',5) ) as v (highway,prio) on v.highway=l.highway where p.highway='turning_circle' order by p.way,v.prio ) as turning_circle
(select way,barrier,"natural",man_made from planet_osm_line where barrier is not null or "natural" in ('hedge','cliff') or man_made='embankment') as roads
(select way,barrier,"natural" from planet_osm_polygon where barrier is not null or "natural"='hedge') as barriers
(select way,highway,railway from planet_osm_polygon where highway in ('residential','unclassified','pedestrian','service') or railway='platform' order by z_order,way_area desc) as roads

(select way,highway, case when tunnel in ('yes','true','1') then 'yes'::text else tunnel end as tunnel, case when service in ('parking_aisle','drive-through','driveway') then 'INT-minor'::text else service end as service from planet_osm_line where highway in ('motorway','motorway_link','trunk','trunk_link','primary','primary_link','secondary','secondary_link','tertiary','tertiary_link','residential','unclassified','road','service','living_street') order by z_order) as roads

(select way,highway,railway from planet_osm_polygon where highway in ('residential','unclassified','pedestrian','service','footway','living_street','platform','services') or railway='platform' order by z_order,way_area desc) as roads

(select way,highway,foot,construction, case when tunnel in ('yes','true','1') then 'yes'::text else tunnel end as tunnel, case when bridge in ('yes','true','1','viaduct') then 'yes'::text else bridge end as bridge, case when railway in ('spur','siding') or (railway='rail' and service in ('spur','siding','yard')) then 'spur-siding-yard'::text else railway end as railway, case when service in ('parking_aisle','drive-through','driveway') then 'INT-minor'::text else service end as service from planet_osm_line where highway is not null or railway in ('light_rail','narrow_gauge','funicular','rail','subway','tram','spur','siding','platform','disused','abandoned','construction','miniature','turntable') order by z_order) as roads

(select way,highway, case when tunnel in ('yes','true','1') then 'yes'::text else tunnel end as tunnel, case when railway='preserved' and service in ('spur','siding','yard') then 'INT-preserved-ssy'::text else railway end as railway from planet_osm_roads where highway is not null or (railway is not null and railway!='preserved' and (service is null or service not in ('spur','siding','yard'))) or railway='preserved' order by z_order ) as roads
(select way,name from planet_osm_line where waterway='canal' and bridge in ('yes','true','1','aqueduct') order by z_order) as water

(select way,access,highway, case when service in ('parking_aisle','drive-through','driveway') then 'INT-minor'::text end as service from planet_osm_line where access is not null and highway is not null and (bridge is null or bridge not in ('yes','true','1','viaduct')) ) as access

(select way, case when oneway in ('yes','true','1') then 'yes'::text else oneway end as oneway from planet_osm_line where oneway is not null and (highway is not null or railway is not null or waterway is not null) and (bridge is null or bridge not in ('yes','true','1','viaduct')) ) as directions
(select way,highway,name from planet_osm_line where waterway IS NULL and landuse IS NULL and name is not null ) as roads
(select way,place,name from planet_osm_point where place in ('suburb','village','large_village','hamlet','locality','isolated_dwelling','farm') ) as placenames

(select way,highway,ref,char_length(ref) as length from planet_osm_roads where highway in ('motorway','trunk','primary','secondary') and ref is not null and char_length(ref) between 1 and 8 ) as roads

(select way,highway,ref,char_length(ref) as length, case when bridge in ('yes','true','1') then 'yes'::text else bridge end as bridge from planet_osm_line where (highway is not null) and ref is not null and char_length(ref) between 1 and 8 ) as roads
(select way from planet_osm_line where "addr:interpolation" is not null) as interpolation
